==English==
===Etymology===
From Hebrew שָׂטָן (standard Hebrew: Satan, Tiberian Hebrew: Śāṭān), Aramaic שִׂטְנָא (Śiṭnâ), adversary, accuser

===Proper noun===
'''Satan'''

#The [[devil]].

